{"tid":1679978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸客撕台中市連儂牆被捕 晚間遭逐出境5年內不得赴台","createTime":"2019-10-28T13:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:10:57.000Z","uid":28114,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fce1ef297f6b8fe2c15fbcfc0fe1ceda07e3d9a8","tid":1679978,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"台中市美村路地下道連儂牆昨日遭35歲的胡姓大陸男子撕爛文宣，路過台灣市民攔住胡男並報警，台中市警方蒐集人證物證後，全案移送法辦。台中地檢署今天表示，審酌胡男犯案後有悔意，檢方諭知將緩起訴處分，裁定捐款3萬元新台幣（下同，約7,667港元）給公益團體、接受1場法治教育，並限制出境；在緩起訴案件偵結前，須每日到台中地檢署報到。<br />\n<br />\n移民署晚間指出，檢方處分完畢後，將依據《台灣地區與大陸地區人民關係條例》第18條規定，於今晚強制胡男出境，並管制其於5年內不得再度來台。<br />\n<br />\n發起台中連儂牆的成員陳致豪，事後在facebook上感謝見義勇為的民眾，並表示原則很簡單，就是破壞文宣事小，傷害台灣的民主事大，連儂牆撕一貼百，關心香港反送中抗爭的台中市民自然會接力貼上，但用暴力的方式傷害言論自由，無視台灣是法治國家，這樣的行為不能姑息。<br />\n<br />\n陳致豪並稱讚台灣警員有一定水準的法治觀念，不姑息破壞連儂牆的案件，他也呼籲不要再有人以身試法，「不管是政治意見不同的台灣人，或是不曉得哪根筋不對，甚至是別有企圖的中國人，只要破壞連儂牆，壓迫市民的言論表達，我們絕對不會和解，唯一的處理原則就是提告，交由司法處理，台灣是法治國家，不容中國人挑釁，這是大是大非，也是我們和中國很不一樣的地方，我們絕對會如此堅持。」<br />\n<br />\n民進黨台中市議員江肇國奉勸，如果「中國朋友」看了連儂牆上聲援香港言論自由的內容，會抓狂、歇斯底里，就不要再來台灣了，「台灣不歡迎沒有民主素養的人，台灣的民主自由不是你享受的（得）起的！」<br />\n<br />\n此前，有大陸男子在台灣大學撕毀連儂牆標語而遭遞解出境的案例。大陸男子李紹東10月以自由行名義在台旅遊期間，撕毀台灣大學連儂牆標語，被警方移送往台北地檢署偵辦；李紹東被台北地檢署傳召問話時道歉認錯，檢察官決定作出「暫緩起訴」決定，李的家屬繳交3萬元新台幣罰金後，被強制送上飛機遞解出境，5年內不准再踏足台灣。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191028/60203453?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F60203453%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD5%2FPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=d2a48e0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191028%2F60203453%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=94b7fe24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191028/60203453?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d84380c1c7ba5227d285cb439302ff5d8dd63642","tid":1679978,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"狂賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebd01f705c1bf531eccb073962b9af3e665d2ca","tid":1679978,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75eb771d610232e9edf2ea2261a5ebaf84040a6","tid":1679978,"uid":65952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"又多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fecccba2c703c4df618071cb74657b1ca93fd49","tid":1679978,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b93e431fe819e54e43a47f7f8a1b3944f313468","tid":1679978,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191028/large/1572243563_c9d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572243563_c9d2.jpg&h=9f428d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在台中撕紙的胡姓大陸男子被台警攔下，帶回偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191028/large/1572243563_8359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572243563_8359.jpg&h=ebbc0ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撕紙的胡姓大陸男子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191028/large/1572243563_f125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191028%2Flarge%2F1572243563_f125.jpg&h=f64f5057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民進黨市議員江肇國怒批撕毀連儂牆海報的陸客沒有民主素養，台灣不歡迎他們。"},{"pid":"4d156facbf1dde199cdf8de17d7c477e8ea1f317","tid":1679978,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e55a33a7f10970c7a25b6b46fb64599dbc94c6","tid":1679978,"uid":324246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d7d99e1ed46295b93d1255391a331c5c740cee","tid":1679978,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"d0aa2e69dca52ac38841d48125461426129ad6a1","tid":1679978,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"佢地仲停留係第一代牆<br />\n有冇人比d新料佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有牆紙 有連豬連狗 有大型抗爭藝術壁畫"},{"pid":"0a7f3db045b42dfe1d99eebbfa2366706f4faacd","tid":1679978,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"漢奸，法西斯赤納粹黨畜就全是一個沒教養的模樣。"},{"pid":"dd65c1fb8bdf658e0bf18a3d4c8499872bbc743c","tid":1679978,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-